message.text:
My first Tamhunt experience as a Director and as a Co-proponent 🔰

Tamhunt pushed me to step out of my comfort zone and embrace bigger responsibilities. I felt so much excitement and pressure at the same time, but it made the journey even more meaningful. Working with everyone taught me patience, teamwork, and confidence in myself.

Overall, it was a fulfilling journey that I will always remember. I am so thankful for FEU ITHM Student Council for giving me the chance to be a part of this wonderful event. And for FEU SAGA for trusting me to be one of the proponents. Special mention to the EBs, OICs, Co-directors and Co-proponents who guided me throughout the event. 

See me next event? 👀

message.text:
My first Tamhunt experience as a Director and as a Co-proponent 🔰

Tamhunt pushed me to step out of my comfort zone and embrace bigger responsibilities. I felt so much excitement and pressure at the same time, but it made the journey even more meaningful. Working with everyone taught me patience, teamwork, and confidence in myself.

Overall, it was a fulfilling journey that I will always remember. I am so thankful for FEU ITHM Student Council for giving me the chance to be a part of this wonderful event. And for FEU SAGA for trusting me to be one of the proponents. Special mention to the EBs, OICs, Co-directors and Co-proponents who guided me throughout the event. 

See me next event? 👀

message.text:
My first Tamhunt experience as a Director and as a Co-proponent 🔰

Tamhunt pushed me to step out of my comfort zone and embrace bigger responsibilities. I felt so much excitement and pressure at the same time, but it made the journey even more meaningful. Working with everyone taught me patience, teamwork, and confidence in myself.

Overall, it was a fulfilling journey that I will always remember. I am so thankful for FEU ITHM Student Council for giving me the chance to be a part of this wonderful event. And for FEU SAGA for trusting me to be one of the proponents. Special mention to the EBs, OICs, Co-directors and Co-proponents who guided me throughout the event. 

See me next event? 👀

message.text:
#ICYMI | TamAthletes, all in for gold!

Last September 9, the FEU Grounds lit up as TamRally 2025 brought together Tamaraw athletes and supporters for the UAAP Season 88 kickoff. The crowd’s loud chants and vibrant colors set the stage as FEU unveiled its official roster.

Fueled by last season’s runner-up finish, the Tamaraws charge into the new season determined to bring the crown home to the green and gold.

Let's all be brave, as gold is the goal this Season 88! 

Photos and Edited by: Enzo Abello

message.text:
#ICYMI | TamAthletes, all in for gold!

Last September 9, the FEU Grounds lit up as TamRally 2025 brought together Tamaraw athletes and supporters for the UAAP Season 88 kickoff. The crowd’s loud chants and vibrant colors set the stage as FEU unveiled its official roster.

Fueled by last season’s runner-up finish, the Tamaraws charge into the new season determined to bring the crown home to the green and gold.

Let's all be brave, as gold is the goal this Season 88! 

Photos and Edited by: Enzo Abello 

#TamRally2025

message.text:
#ICYMI | Huling Biyahe ng Lakbay Piyu 2025! ✈️✨

Bawat sandali ay parang paglipad patungo sa bagong alaala. Mabilis man o mabagal, bawat tawa at kwento ay nag-iwan ng marka sa ating paglalakbay. 🌍✨

Sa huling dalawang araw ng saya, pagtuklas, at samahan lahat ay hindi malilimutan. 

Naging espesyal ang mga araw na ito dahil sa inyo, Tams! 😊

Photos by: Enzo Abello & Sharlene Rabusa
Edited by: Enzo Abello 

#TamHunt2025

message.text:
#ICYMI | Huling Biyahe ng Lakbay Piyu 2025! ✈️✨

Bawat sandali ay parang paglipad patungo sa bagong alaala. Mabilis man o mabagal, bawat tawa at kwento ay nag-iwan ng marka sa ating paglalakbay. 🌍✨

Sa huling dalawang araw ng saya, pagtuklas, at samahan lahat ay hindi malilimutan. 

Naging espesyal ang mga araw na ito dahil sa inyo, Tams! 😊

Photos by: Enzo Abello & Sharlene Rabusa
Edited by: Enzo Abello 

#TamHunt2025

Sa huling dalawang araw ng saya, pagtuklas, at samahan lahat ay hindi malilimutan. 

Naging espesyal ang mga araw na ito dahil sa inyo, Tams! 😊

Edited by: Enzo Abello
